<p>Things seem complicated when there is a lot of nuance.</p>

<p>For example, mathematics is a notation designed for the 2D problem space of pen-and-paper (x,y).</p>

<p>Anything â€œmore than 2Dâ€ requires mental gymnastics to map from â€œmore than 2D spaceâ€ to â€œ2D-only spaceâ€.</p>

