<ol>
  <li>think that the domain(s) is â€œcomplicatedâ€</li>
  <li>brand the select few with the label â€œsmartâ€.</li>
</ol>

<p>Computers work in 4D space - x, y, z, t<sup id="fnref:1" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:1" class="footnote">1</a></sup>.</p>

<p>Programming would appear to be less-complicated if we used a 4D notation for programming.</p>

